Package bt.data

Interface DataRange

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Range<DataRange>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DelegatingDataRange, SynchronizedDataRange

    public interface DataRange
extends Range<DataRange>
    Represents a range of binary data, abstracting the mapping of data onto the storage layer. Real data may span over several storage units or reside completely inside a single storage unit.
    Since:
    1.2
